Title: Euphoria (2)
Plot: Foreman continues to experience the same progression of symptoms as the police officer. When he realizes he may be facing imminent death, he calls his father who comes to his son's side. As it comes down to a race against time, House believes the solution to the illness is in the police officer's apartment.
Writer: Russel Friend, Garrett Lerner, David Shore
GuestStars: Amber DeMarco, Leigh-Allyn Baker, Scott Michael Campbell, Charles S. Dutton
